    <abstract>
      <t>This document provides a framework to describe how to use current
   existing GMPLS routing and signaling to set up ODUk/ODUflex over
   ODUCn link, as a result of the support of OTU/ODU links with rates
   larger than 100G in the 2016 version of G.709.</t>
